<div class="flex-grid" style="background-color: #fff;color:#000;margin:0;opacity: .85;padding:15px;">
    <div>
        <h3>About Open-Dash</h3>
        <p>An open-source project built from the ground up...</p>
    </div>
    <div class="row cell-auto-size" style="margin-top:20px;">
        <div class="cell size4 padding20">
            <div><h3>Donate</h3>
                <p>Donate your Time, Coding Skills, Design Skills, Testing, feedback or even Money. Â Nothing in life is truely free, and your
                donation will go to fund the development and collaboration resources needed to keep this project going.</p>
                <p>Donations of $25USD or more will get a permanent shout out in our donators section and placement in the source code
                and application screens.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="margin40">
                <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
                    <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
                    <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="74ZLRLLETB45U">
                    <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
                    <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="dashList" class="cell size4 padding20">
            <h3>Existing Dashboards</h3>
            <ul class="simple-list large-bullet">
                {{#each dashboards}}
                <li><a href="/dashboards/{{id}}">{{name}}</a> : <a href="/dashboards/{{id}}/edit">edit</a></li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="cell size4 padding20">
            <h3>Settings</h3>
            <a href="/settings">Go To Settings</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>